data.description: Wow! Sellers approved a lower price! You are going to love this home! Great floor plan with a 22x15 family room and large breakfast area adjoining the kitchen. So many extra details- stone fireplace with custom made mantel, wainscoting in the kitchen, plus crown molding in the living room and kitchen, and trim accents in the foyer. Interior has been freshly painted and this home is move in ready. Laundry room is almost as large as the guest bedroom plenty of space for storage, ironing board, etc.Huge fenced back yard- room to roam. Convenient location to both Greenville and Easley. Lots of storage too! No HOA! Grocery stores and super store nearby.
